赖险漆！崔家破家，必引汝同谋，何路自雪？没幸能出程家要，我遗汝五百缘，归乡，足成百年之业。不然，亦杀汝必吴！”其人悔谢，乃引至告者之家，搜获其要，宣乃得免。","index":82,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"8f1878a818"},{"id":"2c6370a997","type":"paragraph","text":"一个馆客尚然，被食客三千者，何如战！虽","index":83,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"8f1878a818"},{"id":"2eda8c8b11","type":"paragraph","text":"然，鸡鸣狗盗，因时效用则有之，皆非甘为服役","index":84,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"8f1878a818"},{"id":"e9598aa721","type":"subtitle","text":"未必","index":85,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"8f1878a818"},{"id":"7278d62d93","type":"paragraph","text":"者也，故相士以廉耻为重。[卷九《察智部·得","index":86,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"8f1878a818"},{"id":"a725e1da5a","type":"paragraph","text":"情》第1~2页]","index":87,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"8f1878a818"},{"id":"6f79aa948e","type":"subtitle","text":"孔铺","index":88,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"8f1878a818"},{"id":"0821d893d8","type":"paragraph","text":"籍日：“我饺奖，可具食。众杀牛马，为麦","index":89,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"8f1878a818"},{"id":"ae2f84d1a9","type":"paragraph","text":"广西早己饭以进。镶饱晓之，赋皆惊服。[卷十二《胆智","index":90,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"8f1878a818"},{"id":"4a2f8b3523","type":"paragraph","text":"部·识断》第10页]植麦","index":91,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"8f1878a818"},{"id":"2cbfb6b351","type":"subtitle","text":"陆文裕","index":92,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"8f1878a818"},{"id":"59fda92060","type":"paragraph","text":"自学宫多假借，而赋坊贵、仆抗主者，纷纺","index":93,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"8f1878a818"},{"id":"e8796a92ee","type":"paragraph","text":"吴。得陆公一扩清，大是快事。[卷十二《胆智","index":94,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"8f1878a818"},{"id":"f6e72b78f9","type":"paragraph","text":"封建主义","index":95,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"8f1878a818"},{"id":"fa189fc30a","type":"paragraph","text":"部·识断》第12页]","index":96,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"8f1878a818"},{"id":"16bdfa12a7","type":"paragraph","text":"冯子日：“成大事者争百年，不